\c 95
\s Jehovha ngaakudzwe ateererwe navanhu
\p
\v 1 Uyai, tiimbire Jehovha; Ngatipururudzei dombo rokuponeswa kwedu.
\v 2 Ngatisvike pamberi pake tichivonga, Ngatimupururudzei namapisarema,
\v 3 Nokuti Jehovha ndiMwari mukuru, ,Mambo mukuru anokunda vamwari vose.
\v 4 Nzvimbo dzakadzika dzapasi dziri muruoko rwake; Misoro yamakomo ndeyakewo.
\
\v 5 Gungwa nderake, ndiye akariita; Maoko ake akaumba nyika yakaoma.
\p
\v 6 Uyai, tinamate tikotamire pasi; Ngatipfugame pamberi paJehovha Muiti wedu.
\p
\v 7 Nokuti ndiye Mwari wedu,
\s Isu tiri vanhu vanofudzwa naye, namakwai oruoko rwake.
\s Nhasi dai muchinzwa henyu izwi
\s rake!
\s "Regai kuomesa mwoyo yenyu sapaMeribha,
\p Sapazuva reMasa murenje;
\v 9 Panguva yandakaidzwa namadzibaba enyu,
\p Vakandiidza, vakaona zvandakaita.
\v 10 Ndakanza ndine shune iatuusqt:+
\v 0
\s porudzi urwo makore makumi mana,
\s Ndikati, `Ndivanhu vakarashika pamwoyo yavo,
\p Havana kuziva nzira dzangu;'
\v 11 Saka ndakapika pakutsamwa kwangu, ndikati,
\s `Havangazopindi pazororo rangu.' "
